  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.3">
<l>neyyā rāḻiyuñ caṅkamu mēntum nīṇṭa tōḷuṭai yāyaṭi yēṉaic</l>
<l>ceyyā tavula kattiṭaic ceytāy ciṟumaik kumperu maikkumuḷ pukuntu</l>
<l>poyyā laivareṉ meykuṭi yēṟip pōṟṟi vāḻvataṟ kañciniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>aiyā niṉṉaṭi yaṉṟimaṟ ṟaṟiyē ṉaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with long arms who bears the conch and blood-stained discus,</l>
<l>Within [this] world, you did to me, your servant,</l>
<l rend="indent">[something] that is not done;</l>
<l>Fearing living [a life] that the five senses sustain through delusion,</l>
<l rend="indent">having crept into [everything] large and small,</l>
<l rend="indent">having taken up residence in my body,</l>
<l>I took refuge in you, master. Besides your feet, I do not know any[thing] other,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
